{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-template-js","path":"/REDUX/0110/","result":{"data":{"cur":{"id":"c9b96ffc-855c-53d5-bff1-9040c11c9759","html":"<h4 id=\"기존에-사용했던-recoil-이외의-전역상태관리-라이브러리인-redux를-학습하며-정리합니다\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EA%B8%B0%EC%A1%B4%EC%97%90-%EC%82%AC%EC%9A%A9%ED%96%88%EB%8D%98-recoil-%EC%9D%B4%EC%99%B8%EC%9D%98-%EC%A0%84%EC%97%AD%EC%83%81%ED%83%9C%EA%B4%80%EB%A6%AC-%EB%9D%BC%EC%9D%B4%EB%B8%8C%EB%9F%AC%EB%A6%AC%EC%9D%B8-redux%EB%A5%BC-%ED%95%99%EC%8A%B5%ED%95%98%EB%A9%B0-%EC%A0%95%EB%A6%AC%ED%95%A9%EB%8B%88%EB%8B%A4\" aria-label=\"기존에 사용했던 recoil 이외의 전역상태관리 라이브러리인 redux를 학습하며 정리합니다 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>기존에 사용했던 recoil 이외의 전역상태관리 라이브러리인 redux를 학습하며 정리합니다.</h4>\n<h1 id=\"useselector\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#useselector\" aria-label=\"useselector permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>useSelector()</h1>\n<p>useSelector는 Redux store로부터 state를 가져올 때 사용한다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">import {createStore} from \"redux\";\r\n\r\nconst store = createStore(reducer);\r\n\r\nexport default store;\r\n</code></pre></div>\n<h1 id=\"usedispatch\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#usedispatch\" aria-label=\"usedispatch permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>useDispatch()</h1>\n<p>useDispatch는 action을 reducer로 dispatch할 때 사용할 수 있는 훅이다. (reducer로 dispatch하여 기존의 state를 <code class=\"language-text\">대체</code>한다)</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">import {useDispatch} from \"react-redux\"\r\n\r\nconst dispatch = useDispatch();\r\n\r\ndispatch(ACTION)</code></pre></div>\n<hr/>\n<h3 id=\"리덕스-작업을-위해서는-3개의-파일을-생성해야-한다\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EB%A6%AC%EB%8D%95%EC%8A%A4-%EC%9E%91%EC%97%85%EC%9D%84-%EC%9C%84%ED%95%B4%EC%84%9C%EB%8A%94-3%EA%B0%9C%EC%9D%98-%ED%8C%8C%EC%9D%BC%EC%9D%84-%EC%83%9D%EC%84%B1%ED%95%B4%EC%95%BC-%ED%95%9C%EB%8B%A4\" aria-label=\"리덕스 작업을 위해서는 3개의 파일을 생성해야 한다 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>리덕스 작업을 위해서는 3개의 파일을 생성해야 한다.</h3>\n<blockquote>\n<li/>action   \n</blockquote>\n<blockquote>\n<p>action을 생성하고, 해당 action이 어떤 일을 수행할지 지정한다.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<blockquote>\n<li/>reducer   \n</blockquote>\n<blockquote>\n<p>dispatch된 action을 실행시킬 reducer\r\naction 객체를 받아 기존의 state를 대체시킨다.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<blockquote>\n<li/>store   \n</blockquote>\n<blockquote>\n<p>reducer로 <code class=\"language-text\">global store</code>를 만든다</p>\n</blockquote>\n<br/>\n<h4 id=\"간단한-todo-list를-만들기-위해-todo를-추가하고-삭제하는-action을-만든다\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EA%B0%84%EB%8B%A8%ED%95%9C-todo-list%EB%A5%BC-%EB%A7%8C%EB%93%A4%EA%B8%B0-%EC%9C%84%ED%95%B4-todo%EB%A5%BC-%EC%B6%94%EA%B0%80%ED%95%98%EA%B3%A0-%EC%82%AD%EC%A0%9C%ED%95%98%EB%8A%94-action%EC%9D%84-%EB%A7%8C%EB%93%A0%EB%8B%A4\" aria-label=\"간단한 todo list를 만들기 위해 todo를 추가하고 삭제하는 action을 만든다 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>간단한 todo-list를 만들기 위해 todo를 추가하고 삭제하는 action을 만든다.</h4>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">export const add_todo = (todo) => {\r\n    return {\r\n        type:ADD,\r\n        todo:{\r\n            id: id++,\r\n            title: todo.title,\r\n            isComplete: todo.isComplete,\r\n        }\r\n    }\r\n};\r\n\r\nexport const delete_todo = (id) => {\r\n    return {\r\n        type: DELETE,\r\n        id,\r\n    }\r\n};</code></pre></div>\n<p>todo를 추가하기위해 매개변수로 받은 todo 객체를 reducer에게 반환하고, todo를 삭제하기 위해서는 삭제하려는 todo의 id만을 넘겨준다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">const initialState = {\r\n    todos:[],\r\n};\r\n\r\n// action을 받아서 새로운 객체를 형성하고, store의 객체를 대체한다\r\nexport const reducers = (state = initialState, action) => {\r\n    if (action.type === ADD){\r\n        return{\r\n            todos:[...state.todos, action.todo],\r\n        };\r\n    }\r\n    \r\n    if (action.type === DELETE) {\r\n        return {\r\n            todos:[...state.todos.filter((todo) => todo.id !== action.id)]\r\n        }\r\n    }\r\n\r\n}</code></pre></div>\n<blockquote>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">[ADD]</code>initialState로 todos라는 빈 배열을 만들고, 이 배열에 새로운 항목을 추가한 <code class=\"language-text\">새로운 state</code>를 반환하도록 한다.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<blockquote>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">[DELETE]</code>action이 넘겨줄 id를 가지고 <code class=\"language-text\">Array.filter()</code> 메서드를 이용해 id가 동일한 todo 객체를 삭제한 todos를 반환하도록 한다.`</p>\n</blockquote>\n<h3 id=\"store\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#store\" aria-label=\"store permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>store</h3>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">import {createStore} from \"redux\";\r\n\r\nconst store = createStore(reducer);\r\n\r\nexport default store;</code></pre></div>\n<p>리덕스 store에 reducer를 넣어주는 작업을 해당 파일에서 수행한다.</p>\n<h2 id=\"inputform\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#inputform\" aria-label=\"inputform permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>InputForm</h2>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">export default function InputForm() {\r\n\r\n    const dispatch = useDispatch();\r\n    const [text, setText] = useState(\"\");\r\n\r\n    const handleChange = (e: any) => {\r\n        const {value} = e.target;\r\n        setText(value);\r\n        // console.log(\"text\", text)\r\n    };\r\n\r\n    const handleClick = () => {\r\n        if (text.trim() === ''){\r\n            alert(\"글자를 입력해주세요\");\r\n            return;\r\n        };\r\n        const todo = {\r\n            title: text,\r\n            isComplete:false,\r\n        }\r\n        // action을 dispatch\r\n        dispatch(add_todo(todo));\r\n        alert(\"입력되었습니다\");\r\n        setText(\"\");\r\n\r\n    };\r\n\r\n    const handleKeyPress = (e:any) => {\r\n        if(e.key === \"Enter\"){\r\n            handleClick();\r\n        }\r\n    };\r\n\r\n\r\n  return (\r\n    &lt;Wrapper>\r\n        &lt;Input placeholder='Write down your todos' onChange={handleChange} onKeyDown={handleKeyPress}/>\r\n        &lt;Buttons onClick={handleClick}>Add&lt;/Buttons>\r\n    &lt;/Wrapper>\r\n  )\r\n}</code></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"todoitem\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#todoitem\" aria-label=\"todoitem permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>todoItem</h2>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">export default function TodoItem({todo}) {\r\n    const dispatch = useDispatch();\r\n\r\n    const {id, title, isComplete} = todo;\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n    // action(delete_todo)을 dispatch한다.\r\n    const handleClick = () => {\r\n        dispatch(delete_todo(id))\r\n    }\r\n  return (\r\n    &lt;Wrapper>\r\n      &lt;input type=\"checkbox\" onClick={handleCheck}/>\r\n        &lt;Title>{title}&lt;/Title>\r\n        {/* &lt;div onClick={handleClick}>x&lt;/div> */}\r\n        &lt;IconWrapper>\r\n          &lt;BsPen style={{cursor:'pointer', marginRight:'20px'}}/>\r\n          &lt;BsTrash onClick={handleClick} style={{cursor:'pointer'}}/>\r\n        &lt;/IconWrapper>\r\n    &lt;/Wrapper>\r\n  )\r\n}</code></pre></div>\n<p>여기에서는 todo item을 삭제, 즉 해당 todo를 완료했을 경우를 위해 DELETE ACTION을 dispatch한다. 이를 위해 useDispatch()를 사용했다.</p>\n<h2 id=\"todolist\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#todolist\" aria-label=\"todolist permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>todoList</h2>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">export default function TodoList() {\r\n    const todos = useSelector((state:any) => state?.todos);\r\n\r\n  return (\r\n        &lt;Wrapper>\r\n          {todos?.map((todo:any) => (\r\n              &lt;TodoItem key={todo.id} todo={todo}>&lt;/TodoItem>\r\n          ))}\r\n         &lt;/Wrapper>\r\n    \r\n  )\r\n}</code></pre></div>","excerpt":"기존에 사용했던 recoil 이외의 전역상태관리 라이브러리인 redux를 학습하며 정리합니다. useSelector() useSelector는 Redux store로부터 state를 가져올 때 사용한다. useDispatch() useDispatch는 action을 reducer로 dispatch할 때 사용할 수 있는 훅이다. (reducer로 dispatch하여 기존의 state를 한다) 리덕스 작업을 위해서는 3개의 파일을 생성해야 한다. action을 생성하고, 해당 action이 어떤 일을 수행할지 지정한다. dispatch된 action을 실행시킬 reducer\r\naction 객체를 받아 기존의 state를 대체시킨다. reducer로 를 만든다 간단한 todo-list를 만들기 위해 todo를 추가하고 삭제하는 action을 만든다. todo를 추가하기위해 매개변수로 받은 todo 객체를 reducer에게 반환하고, todo를 삭제하기 위해서는 삭제하려는 todo의 id…","frontmatter":{"date":"January 10, 2023","title":"Redux로 todo-list 만들기","categories":"Redux","author":"권형석","emoji":"📚"},"fields":{"slug":"/REDUX/0110/"}},"next":{"id":"fee12c60-47fa-5ad1-8958-b8bf296da02b","html":"<h1 id=\"redux\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#redux\" aria-label=\"redux permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Redux</h1>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">state</code>를 관리하는 도구<br>\n<code class=\"language-text\">store</code>라는 저장소에서 component들의 state를 관리한다.<br>\ncomponent가 많아지고 관리해야하는 state가 많아지면 props drilling 문제가 발생한다.<br>\nredux를 사용하게 되면 모든 component에서 <code class=\"language-text\">reducer함수</code>와 <code class=\"language-text\">action</code>을 통해 state에 접근할 수 있다.\r\n<br/></p>\n<h1 id=\"redux로-state-관리하는-방법\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#redux%EB%A1%9C-state-%EA%B4%80%EB%A6%AC%ED%95%98%EB%8A%94-%EB%B0%A9%EB%B2%95\" aria-label=\"redux로 state 관리하는 방법 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Redux로 state 관리하는 방법</h1>\n<p>action을 dispatch하면 reducer함수를 호출한다.<br>\nreducer는 store에 가서 현재 state값을 가져와 새로운 state 객체를 만들고 기존에 존재하던 default state 객체를 <code class=\"language-text\">대체</code>한다</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 720px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 53.888888888888886%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"redux1.png\"\n        title=\"redux1.png\"\n        src=\"/static/2c2083ddb0acdc3aed9b72262d80dda0/37523/redux1.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/2c2083ddb0acdc3aed9b72262d80dda0/e9ff0/redux1.png 180w,\n/static/2c2083ddb0acdc3aed9b72262d80dda0/f21e7/redux1.png 360w,\n/static/2c2083ddb0acdc3aed9b72262d80dda0/37523/redux1.png 720w,\n/static/2c2083ddb0acdc3aed9b72262d80dda0/302a4/redux1.png 1080w,\n/static/2c2083ddb0acdc3aed9b72262d80dda0/07a9c/redux1.png 1440w,\n/static/2c2083ddb0acdc3aed9b72262d80dda0/cea38/redux1.png 1644w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 720px) 100vw, 720px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n    </span>\r\n<br/>\r\n<span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 720px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 57.77777777777777%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"redux2.png\"\n        title=\"redux2.png\"\n        src=\"/static/b7faa7a01ea56680f718b874ae05a8a7/37523/redux2.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/b7faa7a01ea56680f718b874ae05a8a7/e9ff0/redux2.png 180w,\n/static/b7faa7a01ea56680f718b874ae05a8a7/f21e7/redux2.png 360w,\n/static/b7faa7a01ea56680f718b874ae05a8a7/37523/redux2.png 720w,\n/static/b7faa7a01ea56680f718b874ae05a8a7/302a4/redux2.png 1080w,\n/static/b7faa7a01ea56680f718b874ae05a8a7/07a9c/redux2.png 1440w,\n/static/b7faa7a01ea56680f718b874ae05a8a7/09b15/redux2.png 1704w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 720px) 100vw, 720px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<h2 id=\"state\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#state\" aria-label=\"state permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>state</h2>\n<blockquote>\n<p>기본 객체</p>\n</blockquote>\n<h2 id=\"action\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#action\" aria-label=\"action permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>action</h2>\n<p>기본값인 state를 바꾸는것\r\ndispatch로 action을 객체에 <code class=\"language-text\">전달</code>한다.</p>\n<blockquote>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">dispatch({type:TEST});\r\n\r\n//data 추가\r\ndispatch({type:TEST, data:'test'})</code></pre></div>\n</blockquote>\n<h2 id=\"dispatch\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#dispatch\" aria-label=\"dispatch permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>dispatch</h2>\n<blockquote>\n<p>이전 action으로 돌아갈 수 있는 타임머신 기능과 어떤 동작이 취해졌는지에 대한 history가 제공되기 때문에 에러 핸들링이 쉬워진다.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<h2 id=\"reducer\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#reducer\" aria-label=\"reducer permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Reducer</h2>\n<p>action이 실행되면 Reducer에서 새로운 객체가 생성되고, 기존 store의 state 객체가 새로운 객체로 <code class=\"language-text\">대체</code>된다.\r\naction을 받아서 새로운 state를 만들어주는 역할\r\ndispatch된 액션이 reducer에 걸리고, 다음 state를 만들어낸다.</p>\n<blockquote>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">export const TEST = 'TEST';\r\n\r\nconst rootReducer = (state=0,action){\r\n switch(action.type){\r\n    case TEST\r\n    return state+1\r\n    dafult:\r\n    return state\r\n }\r\n}</code></pre></div>\n<p>action을 dispatch하면 reducer함수가 호출이되는데<br>\ndispatch로 전달된 action.type에 따라 실행할 코드를 작성하면<br>\n이전 state에서 변경된 state를 확인하여\r\n<code class=\"language-text\">새로운 state 객체</code>를 반환해준다.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<h2 id=\"store\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#store\" aria-label=\"store permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Store</h2>\n<blockquote>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">import {createStore} from 'redux';\r\nexport const TEST = 'TEST';\r\n\r\nconst rootReducer = (state=0,action){\r\n switch(action.type){\r\n   case TEST\r\n     return state+1\r\n   dafult:\r\n    return state\r\n }\r\n}\r\n\r\nconst store = redux.createStore( rootReducer );//store 생성\r\nconsole.log(store.getState())//0 (현재 state 가져오기)\r\n\r\nstore.dispath({type:TEST})\r\nconsole.log(store.getState())//1</code></pre></div>\n<p>createStore로 store를 만들고</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>reducer에서 새로운 state값 반환하면<br>\nstore에 저장되어 있는 현재 state값이 업데이트된다.\r\n<br/>\r\n<br/>\r\nstore는 state를 관리해주고<br>\ngetState()는 메서드로 현재 state를 가져오며<br>\ndispatch를 통해 state를 업데이트할 수 있다.<br>\n<br/>\r\n<br/>\r\n그리고 store가 변경되면 dispatch가 store의 subscribe메서드를 통해<br>\n변경된 state값으로 다시 render해주게 된다.<br>\n그러면 변경된 ui로 stater값이 바뀌게된다.</p>","frontmatter":{"date":"January 05, 2023","title":"Redux","categories":"Redux","author":"권형석","emoji":"📚"},"fields":{"slug":"/REDUX/0105/"}},"prev":{"id":"ab83d630-9bf2-5734-83f0-46eb5ce05b5e","html":"<h2 id=\"typescript-타이핑-과정-중에-발생한-에러\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#typescript-%ED%83%80%EC%9D%B4%ED%95%91-%EA%B3%BC%EC%A0%95-%EC%A4%91%EC%97%90-%EB%B0%9C%EC%83%9D%ED%95%9C-%EC%97%90%EB%9F%AC\" aria-label=\"typescript 타이핑 과정 중에 발생한 에러 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>TypeScript 타이핑 과정 중에 발생한 에러</h2>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 708px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 41.11111111111111%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"1.png\"\n        title=\"1.png\"\n        src=\"/static/e4c8d1f4a01dcd495d71d3a0f1f58472/3cb0f/1.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/e4c8d1f4a01dcd495d71d3a0f1f58472/e9ff0/1.png 180w,\n/static/e4c8d1f4a01dcd495d71d3a0f1f58472/f21e7/1.png 360w,\n/static/e4c8d1f4a01dcd495d71d3a0f1f58472/3cb0f/1.png 708w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 708px) 100vw, 708px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>사실 ESLint에서 발생하는 오류라서 실행은 정상적으로 되지만, 거슬리기 때문에 해결하기 위해 구글링을 했다.\r\n<br/></p>\n</blockquote>\n<h1 id=\"해결방법\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%ED%95%B4%EA%B2%B0%EB%B0%A9%EB%B2%95\" aria-label=\"해결방법 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>해결방법</h1>\n<ol>\n<li>먼저, ESLint 자체에서 해결하기 위해 .eslint.js를 연다.</li>\n<li>다음과 같은 문구를 추가한다.</li>\n</ol>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">  rules: {\r\n        'prettier/prettier': [\r\n            'error',\r\n            {\r\n                endOfLine: 'auto',\r\n            },\r\n        ],\r\n    },</code></pre></div>\n<br/>\r\n다음과 같이 에러가 해결되었다!   \r\n<br/>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 711px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 41.11111111111111%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"2.png\"\n        title=\"2.png\"\n        src=\"/static/960120b3924f1cb2f91d6043c38103ff/a8e5b/2.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/960120b3924f1cb2f91d6043c38103ff/e9ff0/2.png 180w,\n/static/960120b3924f1cb2f91d6043c38103ff/f21e7/2.png 360w,\n/static/960120b3924f1cb2f91d6043c38103ff/a8e5b/2.png 711w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 711px) 100vw, 711px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n    </span></p>","frontmatter":{"date":"January 10, 2023","title":"Delete `␍`eslintprettier/prettier","categories":"Error, TypeScript","author":"권형석","emoji":"👾"},"fields":{"slug":"/TIL/0110/"}},"site":{"siteMetadata":{"siteUrl":"https://hskwon5170.github.io","comments":{"utterances":{"repo":""}}}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/REDUX/0110/","nextSlug":"/REDUX/0105/","prevSlug":"/TIL/0110/"}},"staticQueryHashes":["1073350324","1956554647","2938748437"]}